metadata.description:
f(hash) = singularity
A glimpse on the primitive expansion of time and space.

500000 particles, pure JS/WebGL/ThreeJS code

Press 'B' to see the primitive expansion animation
Press 'S' to save a 4K PNG of current view (4096x2304)

metadata.name: Random and Shapes #21
metadata.description:
Random is the most basic and essential tool in generative art. Yet with many different parameters, beautiful works could still be achievable with only random numbers.

This project is associated with a generative art course at NCCU in Taiwan.

metadata.name: Wildwood Forest #933
metadata.description:
The Trees are the embodiment of a sanctorium. Anyone who knows how to speak to them and listen to them can embrace the truth. they preach the ancient law of life. Under these trees bushes that generate the flow of life in the darkened celestial sphere , with the greatest sun of spring's clear weather and again in fall when every leaf is a flower. And what magnificent bouquets the autumn leaves make.

Enjoy :)

---
Created using vanilla javascript
KrouniHatim - Nov22

metadata.name: BINARY WORDS #286
metadata.description:
I drew my first 8x8 pixel binary image on 11/08/2022 with 'iloveyou' encoded for my wife, it was our 10-year anniversary on this day.  After that made this generative stuff for fxhash's birthday bash.

#fxhashturnsone

Donations:
25% to ThreeJs team

The image contains a binary coded word or phrase with a length of 8 characters. The grays represents 0, the other colors represents 1. One row -> one character. Should be proceed decoding from left to right and from top to bottom.

An example: 'iloveyou'

01101001
01101100
01101111
01110110
01100101
01111001
01101111
01110101

The fxrandom selects a word and the program converts it to binary data. After that, the background (ground and sky) is randomly generated from color schemes. Then the binary gray colors are drawn. Also the color of light next to null colors is randomly generated from color schemes. Random affects also the animation.

The animation stops when you do these interactions below, then restarts after a few seconds of inactivity.

Press spacebar to change:

- frame view -> without frame
- without frame -> original 8x8px size
- original 8x8px size -> frame view

Press 's' to save an svg from current view.

Notes:
- Build with ReactJs and TweenJs
- Every upcoming day, half of the remaining pieces are burned.

Happy Birthday fxhash community!
I'm glad to be among you!
